@deffn {Function} {clim-extensions:draw-glyph} sheet string x y &rest args &key align-x align-y toward-x toward-y transform-glyphs ink clipping-region transformation text-style text-family text-face text-size
@findex clim-extensions:draw-glyph
Draws a single character of filled text represented by the given
element.  element is a character or other object to be translated
into a font index.  The given x and y specify the left baseline
position for the character.
@end deffn
